      </h2>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        In 2025, S&P Global surveyed 1,000+ enterprises. The results? <strong>42% abandoned most AI initiatives.</strong>
        Here's why—and how to avoid becoming a statistic:
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-red-600 mb-2">80%</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-red-900 mb-2">Failure Rate</p>
          <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">RAND Corporation: AI projects fail at 2x the rate of other tech initiatives</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-600 mb-2">64%</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-orange-900 mb-2">Feel Overwhelmed</p>
          <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm">Employees cite "integrating AI into daily work" as top challenge</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-yellow-600 mb-2">47%</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-2">Feel Unprepared</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Nearly half of workers don't know how to achieve expected productivity gains</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-purple-600 mb-2">75%</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-purple-900 mb-2">Job Security Fears</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Employees worry AI could render their roles obsolete</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Core Problem (Informatica CDO Survey 2025):</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg">
