            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 italic mb-4">
            "Dave's training took us from 'we can't use AI because security' to saving 22 hours per employee per week in 8 weeks.
            The ROI was undeniable by Week 3. Our CISO is now our biggest AI champion."
